text: I am okay following the train collision. Grateful for the swift action by my colleagues and first responders as they work to assist the injured. Please continue to pray for everyone involved.

Under the Trump Administration, we're working to restore our Nation's military readiness and warfighting capabilities. After years of consistent neglect, I'm proud to have an ally in the White House who recognizes the importance of a well-funded Armed Services. #SOTU @POTUS

Since the beginning of this Congress, House and Senate Republicans have rolled back dozens of burdensome, Obama-era regulations that have stifled growth and hiked up costs. In fact, in 2017 alone, more than 600 regulations were withdrawn! It's time to unleash American innovation!

In the the wake of the #TaxCutsandJobsAct, $3 billion in bonuses have been doled out by corporations across the country, including #Georgia-based businesses like @SunTrust, @Aflac, and @HomeDepot! Looking forward to continued growth under @POTUS Donald Trump. #SOTU
